	* if.h: (if_lookup_by_name_len, if_get_by_name_len) New functions.
	* if.c: (if_lookup_by_name_len, if_get_by_name_len) New functions.
	  (if_get_by_name) Tighten up code.
	  (interface) Use new function if_get_by_name_len.
