	zebra_ipv4_add(), zebra_ipv4_delete() are removed.

	* routemap.c (route_map_empty): Add new function.
	(route_map_delete): Use route_map_index_delete() instead of
	route_map_index_free().
	(route_map_index_free): Function removed.

